{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"be8b19fee9","title":"大字报诗——致勇敢的战士","origin":"《毒草集》(内部资料·注意保存)，中共武汉水利学院委员会宣传部编，1957年8月25日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"503ae064da","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"be8b19fee9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"027a584078","name":"武汉水利学院学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9349429b2d","type":"title","text":"大字报诗——致勇敢的战士","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"6560f20943","type":"authors","text":"武汉水利学院学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"fac9d8cd08","type":"subtitle","text":"致勇敢的战士　　　　·小兵·","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"c31623f317","type":"paragraph","text":"我们不是勇敢的战士，","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"5bba02db00","type":"paragraph","text":"只是一个平凡的小兵，","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"2c8793fa2e","type":"paragraph","text":"我们不愿追问“居心何在？”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"6fac115429","type":"paragraph","text":"也不愿意“咄咄逼人”，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"9b430b6bf6","type":"paragraph","text":"我们不需要“大民主”，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"5cb6e859a0","type":"paragraph","text":"也反对拖拉不改“官僚主义”，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"4ac55c010d","type":"paragraph","text":"我们有几个诚恳的愿望：","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"3f5b25afa4","type":"paragraph","text":"该撤职的撤职，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"2ca55cf145","type":"paragraph","text":"该调薪的适当调整，","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"6a8b0ec8c7","type":"paragraph","text":"从福利金中吸取教训，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"91f4d6068e","type":"paragraph","text":"只后再不要只顾“自己人”的享受，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"75743748b0","type":"paragraph","text":"而忘记了广大群众的贫困，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"5377e1c094","type":"paragraph","text":"几个疑难的案件：","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"f0d4e8e128","type":"paragraph","text":"私改档案，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"85c6b9db0d","type":"paragraph","text":"陷害干部，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"1489001256","type":"paragraph","text":"诱骗少女，","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"16620f1e51","type":"paragraph","text":"推下历承根，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"014645dfb6","type":"paragraph","text":"都希望早日弄清，","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"8d617d38c7","type":"paragraph","text":"假如是真的，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"72646df1ed","type":"paragraph","text":"就不要让那些罪犯法外，","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"075c7124f0","type":"paragraph","text":"假如是假的，","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"5ccb74ab7f","type":"paragraph","text":"也让我们知道内中详情。","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"b2fb02f6c0","type":"paragraph","text":"(虽然我们不必追问)","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"328577251a","type":"paragraph","text":"我们希望对肃反问题重心估价","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"f70ad9b1e2","type":"paragraph","text":"让成绩和缺点占适当的成分，","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"29da53103d","type":"paragraph","text":"让那些受冤者得到平反，","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"425f1c0e9d","type":"paragraph","text":"让那些“该斗的”得到新生。","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"2512bc0612","type":"paragraph","text":"让那些违法乱纪分子，","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"3fe7285280","type":"paragraph","text":"受到应得的处分。","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"70a7f3abe0","type":"paragraph","text":"我们还有一个最大的愿望：","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"fec16fab12","type":"paragraph","text":"勇敢的战士，","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"8772404b2f","type":"paragraph","text":"望你们团结一致，","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"8e3a36b952","type":"paragraph","text":"领导着我们这些小兵。","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"150a9d0e67","type":"paragraph","text":"共同一致，","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"2945d3a0b3","type":"paragraph","text":"向三害开火，","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"88e52b786a","type":"paragraph","text":"和风细雨，","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"84fce75e3d","type":"paragraph","text":"让雨不停的下，","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"a7968acf47","type":"paragraph","text":"风不住的吹，","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"e7f92a0cc4","type":"paragraph","text":"让我们这些无名小卒，","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"f9f876def9","type":"paragraph","text":"能够在和风细雨中大胆争鸣。","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"cc0c926da2","type":"subtitle","text":"在争鸣中，","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"3e0b23edad","type":"paragraph","text":"让真理抬头，","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"af96b3c443","type":"paragraph","text":"让错误得到纠正，","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"4306fc07f6","type":"paragraph","text":"让“三害”消灭掉，","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"},{"id":"f62f9f2495","type":"subtitle","text":"让我们大伙儿团结得更紧！","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9"}],"page":{"id":"bbde4f5ea2","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"be8b19fee9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}